{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"深山出诊","authors":["黎泉"],"dates":[{"year":1976,"month":6,"day":27}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"深山出诊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云中甩下弯弯路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人影溶进飘飘雾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身背药箱穿过半山云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗洒云海伴雨珠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再翻一座山呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再越一道谷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巡回医生情如火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出诊的脚步多急促。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进村寨不用喊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目光一碰自相熟——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱尼阿妈治好了眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手拉亲人淌泪珠；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿瓦大爹来医腰痛病："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“嗬，这银针一扎病就除！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"傣家大嫂围一块，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细看针灸新挂图；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打预防针的排长串，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小学生争把臂伸出！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碗碗米酒融深情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走来了村寨老支书："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“过去寨里谁生病，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"医也缺来药也无，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修正主义卫生路线坑害人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难熬的日子涩又苦……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可如今，毛主席派来了好‘摩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雅’，＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"‘六·二六’指示照征途！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伙说，怎么办，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的恩情才不辜负？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“抓革命、促生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永走大寨朝阳路！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人群喧嚷涌田间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象条出山的大瀑布……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月圆了，星出了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家争拉医生宿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“南岭北寨在等着咱呵”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——朗朗笑声留不住。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支书喊：“山箐里野猪在磨牙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要提防拦路的豺和虎！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点起松明火把送亲人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条金龙出山谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——笑声一路歌一路……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊摩雅：傣语，医生。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}